(1136, 182, 'creating_ophthalmologists_description', '<div class=\"ophthalmologists-title clear-both\"><span>Training Programs & Skill Transfer</span></div><div class=\"ophthalmologists-content clear-both\"><p>In addition to eye care, the hospital also conducts short-term and long-term fellowship programs that help practicing ophthalmologists upgrade their skills. Under the skill transfer program, the hospital has trained over 600 ophthalmologists nominated by the Government of India, as well as private ophthalmologists from India and abroad. </p><p><button class=\"learn-more\">Apply Now</button></p></div>'),
